Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論男生女生都很崇拜她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然城裡是很恐怖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道會有什麼發生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找到啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.23,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)}#02 蘿莉小姑也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.23,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)\bord8\3c&HF2C855&}#02 蘿莉小姑也不錯嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}真～白～碳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}在學校的時候為什麼那麼見外呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不論在家還是在學校都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你來學生會室的話 可是有茶和點心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 上鈎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅茶啊不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該請真白碳喝跟你相配的皇家奶茶才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後再配上司康餅怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放上滿滿的濃縮奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 奶茶的話還是果醬好些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}控制好甜度手工製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司康餅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}濃縮奶油？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用我能聽懂的詞說！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我果然還是不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的紅緒在學校居然那麼有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭啦 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是事實啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就不能再謙虛點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而…而且因為是學生會長就把學生會室當成私有地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在學校裡悠閒的喝茶什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是只會出現在漫畫中的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現實怎麼可能會有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來你也憧憬過這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好可愛啊 真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白怎麼會來上高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰家到底是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的也並不詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過貌似是個歷史悠久的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且 幼女高中生不也很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蘿莉小姑也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都說不知道了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 紅緒怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易和小紅住在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起聊聊天什麼的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我居然說些自己都覺得不可能的事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然有了未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有了小姑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小姑明明怎麼看都像小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}實際上卻是個高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要吃藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要擦汗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝雞蛋酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要卷蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是…插進去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 沒事啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像你看到的在查東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有手機的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}離開家的時候給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是和白夜共用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司康餅和濃縮奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不後悔 我才不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}零食就是要限制為仙貝鹹菜什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是想吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次做給你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好有別人送的果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不是什麼太難做的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真 真是不錯的未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然連英國的點心也會做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是在誇我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個家的家務都是小紅做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 母親大人有工作每天很晚才能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人並不擅長這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不討厭做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漢堡排哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漢堡排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我覺得這是不輸給咖哩很好的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整個來炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來不只咖哩 漢堡排也很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}菜譜裡沒有納豆和山藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我可沒說過我討厭納豆和山藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考慮太多的妻子會被厭惡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜歡咖哩和漢堡排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們家的食物主要是和食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像小時候去過你們家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過不怎麼記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 那麼那時候的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胡蘿蔔也要都吃光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 那時候發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能說以前的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜你那時候還受傷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是小紅卻完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅是因為白夜才得救的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我好好的保護了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅她就不會受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是白夜的責任呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為那是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且如果知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅也許會為了自己得救而回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我做蛋包飯 蓋澆飯 義大利麵什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是老樣子憧憬西餐啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不記得的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為那件事的愧疚而結婚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得不該是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我受傷的事我希望你不要對小紅說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她會更在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起來一直發呆卻考慮的很周全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要做司康餅的話奶油不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天去買點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白上高中這件事竟然誰都沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人 姐姐大人 真由良和學校的大家都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我也不覺得想多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}就不要在意細節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFC9A34&\3c&HE8E4E1&\fs60\fad(420,00)\bord10\pos(642,720)}一直想要妹妹的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜真的那樣就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使小紅忘記以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不記得就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}況且那或許是她不願想起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白知道些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是在UFO的歷史中非常有名的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H54FAFB&\3c&H6A81F6&\shad0\pos(824,588)}外星人是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}1952年9月2日的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七位少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}目擊到了神秘的飛行物體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}少年們追上去一看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身高超越3米的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有其他外星人的目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從頭再來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅知道有外星人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很害怕那種節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很有名嗎 外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算是世界聞名的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世界規模？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你原來不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世界上到處都是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會像蟲子一樣湧出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}使用UFO來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從天上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從毫無防備的天上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後把人或者牛帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做人體實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的說法時有時無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 真的很害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有那種事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 喝點牛奶冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從天上來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外星人會把牛帶走擠奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼外星人要體驗擠奶呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這世界上竟然有外星人這種可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家竟然都能安穩的生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未確認生物UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣…不就無計可施了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 等等 我有話要問…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼這麼消沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是…被外星人襲擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼這裡會出現外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就連白夜都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早就超越世界規模…宇宙規模！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟那是外星人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒問到以前的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個時候的事情模模糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且年紀又小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}問誰誰都不肯對我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是被爺爺帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去山上玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去了深山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}深山老林裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很大的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有誰…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼來著…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知不覺睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像是記著的卻想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朦朦朧朧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們知道些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白和白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}問白夜好像也不會有什麼進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得紅緒不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想起UFO和UMA的事情就感到憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…雖然是以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}目光游離好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨晚你好像有話說到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記不記得什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點不疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這點程度沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}傷口清洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之貼上這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬好單純好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}單純？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜同學和真白醬為什麼搬家來這裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為父母的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我因為擔心白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像你看到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直是呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 雖然是擺著一副認真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那完全是在睡覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我有著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有教育小紅的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 因為是妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 別那大聲說那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是小紅做飯和掃除都很擅長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有別的什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}與小姑的交往方式什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然那好像也很擅長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…我覺得小紅做的不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被小姑表揚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然咖哩是辣的不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別的嘛…還差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還是安產型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說中人家在意的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正我就是下半身肥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這又不是什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 又不是胖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}消瘦的人是不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅點心都不吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 那…司康餅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會做的 那個會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吃了就胖 幾乎不吃點心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這段時間因為生日吃了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不補救一下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明不是需要在意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 脂肪都跑到胸部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈哈 是胸部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔喔 那不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}變大一點好處都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起來胖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又要選衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跑起來又痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蹲下又礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 是巨乳最容易說又最不能說的台詞！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論什麼事物一般的就剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在開始會變成什麼樣還不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 那個大概…從家系上看沒什麼希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得有或者沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩邊都有很大的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話題的重心不應該是選出哪邊好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪邊都不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為好像聽到了很愉快的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是紅緒大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又去轉學生的那裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有人認為大小只不過是個性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}簡直就像是…這樣…超越個性的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你這麼說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人好像在說什麼高尚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被洗腦了嗎 這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒是一種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和UMA什麼的一樣是未知物種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人有哪裡奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪裡奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪都奇怪吧！全部都是奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那絕對是使用了洗腦或者集團催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發出了有害電波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定在後腦部的哪裡發送著對人體產生影響的電波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬真的有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前的考試還是全科目100分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種東西可以用等離子體來說明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an7}(P.S. 真白一定是調查了鬼火之類的東西)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還真的調查了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看 這是這個月的校內新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上面也登載了紅緒姐好多的活躍事蹟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因為太厲害了反而低級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在籃球部的比賽上幫忙大活躍？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶頭參加慈善會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成績第一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會的活動也……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼短的時間內竟做了這麼多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有好幾個！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種情況的話 我也很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你一直是這樣想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我人氣高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直擔心怕我被別人搶走是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很嫉妒是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太樂觀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的職業生涯是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為小紅和真白醬的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我將會一直貫徹享受這身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人的話多棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的哦 叫姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 還有 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢 就跟小紅一樣叫姐姐大人就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然也是我指定的這種叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐潔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}指定的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思啊 來配合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底誰是姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜同學也是得叫姐姐大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這件事先放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 真白醬 趕快來學生會玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是說我不去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別說那麼傷人心的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起喝茶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是鳥 還是UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思啊 吵到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會帶她走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒、沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉啊 都是因為紅緒太HIGH了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會好好說她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會也有正常的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬 你害怕UFO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UFO UFO什麼的不存在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不存在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不用說外星人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 我說啊 一直很在意的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個是在小紅家住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 是的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是未婚夫又是同居
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像漫畫一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的 是秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們住在小紅家的事為什麼不能說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是必須要保密的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同居？ 跟紅緒大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個人竟然跟紅緒大人住在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是親戚還可以這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 曝光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還好未婚夫的事情沒曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才說要保密的啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個世界上存在著我們不認識的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道我們只能擔心受怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}與之戰鬥的MDS登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保衛了地球的和平
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下集 感受到愛情喜劇的波動
